==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rim-fire
<hw>Rim"-fire`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having the
percussion fulminate in a rim surrounding the base, distinguished from
<contr>center-fire</contr>; -- said of cartridges; also, using rim-fire
cartridges; <as>as, a <ex>rim-fire</ex> gun</as>. Such cartridges are
now little used.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rimmer</ent>⟦br⟧
